Database Ownership Summary,

I completed the database setup work for the customer churn prediction project using PostgreSQL. My contribution focused on preparing the backend data storage system 
required to store and manage the Telco customer churn dataset. I installed and configured PostgreSQL, created the project database, and designed the required tables 
for storing customer information. I also imported the Telco dataset into the database and verified that the records were inserted correctly. This ensures that the 
project data is stored properly and can be used for further analysis, model training, and churn prediction.
As part of my work, I also checked the database structure and ensured that the customer records were ready for use in the next stages of the project. This database 
setup forms the foundation for connecting the dataset with Python and performing customer churn analysis.

Key Contributions

* Installed and configured PostgreSQL
* Created the project database
* Designed and created customer data tables
* Imported the Telco customer churn dataset
* Verified successful data insertion
* Prepared the database for analysis and prediction tasks
* Supported backend data storage for the churn prediction system

